[Guest]: Yeah, it's heavily influenced by Marathi.

02:36:53.520 --> 02:36:56.940
[Amit Varma]: And first he was in Indore and then he was in Goa where he was outdoor.

02:36:56.940 --> 02:36:59.920
[Unknown]: So that's my dad joke out of the way.

